beauty-sabr-samahah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32083,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Beauty: Islam beautified by patient and tolerance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam is beautified by two qualities: modesty and tolerance for the sake of Allah, and not for anyone else.\u201d Source: al-Tamhi\u0304d li-Ibn 'Abd al-Barr 13\/318 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Ishbili \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32079,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/entire-deen-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":32083,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Haya: All of Islam revolves around modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurrah ibn Iyas reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when modesty was mentioned to him. They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is modesty part of the religion?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cRather, it is the entire religion.\u201d Then, the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, modesty,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5910,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/04\/iman-haya-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":32083,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Iman: Faith and modesty go together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, modesty and faith come together. If one of the two is missing, so is the other.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1313 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/08\/wife-does-duty-enters-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":32083,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Women: A dutiful wife enters Paradise by any gate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a woman prays her five prayers, fasts her month of Ramadan, guards her chastity, and obeys her husband, she will enter Paradise from any gate she wishes.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 4163 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/10\/modesty-is-part-of-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":32083,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Do not admonish him, modesty is part of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a man from the Ansar who was warning his brother about modesty, but the Prophet said, \u201cLet him be, for modesty is part of faith.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 24, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 36 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11676,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/23\/haya-modesty-mind-body-soul\/","url_meta":{"origin":32083,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Be modest with Allah in mind, body, soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe modest before Allah, as is His right.\u201d We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, surely we have modesty, all praise is due to Allah!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is not so. Rather, modesty before Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u063